{"title":"相会在北京","authors":["放平"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":7,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"相会在北京"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在天南，我在地北，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你我同在一个大家庭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是工人，我是农民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗下面结成一家人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在搬砖，我在运瓦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义大厦高了一层，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再高一层。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你也革命，我也革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为国家、为世界，我们奋不顾身。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六亿双粗壮的手，同一颗跃进的心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画出一幅苍松翠柏万年青。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向毛主席汇报，向党中央汇报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风流人物相会在北京。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志啊，亲爱的同志啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见面拉紧手，促膝谈心："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一花先放万花竞放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一处春晓处处迎春。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}